I don't precisely know where the big brother household is. I have a fairly good idea but it's a big forest. Fireworks should work fine for this job. I just roll up a thin piece of cardboard around a screamer to lengthen it. Fill the tube with tiny flyers and stick a pointy end on. Then I repeat this a few times so I have enough of them to be certain atleast one will blow apart above the target.<br>
<br>
A major advantage also is the loud bang. That should definately get everybodies attention. A firework display is kind of hard to ignore and I'll have a TV going in the van to watch the show. A small screamer will should reach the perfect height I'm after.<br>
<br>
Celebrity big brother recently finished. I wasn't able to locate any suitable fireworks in time to raid that particular event but when the next series starts I should be all set up. The most difficult part is cutting out the flyers. It really is a tedious job. <br>
